# Dispute Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   get_card_list — Retrieve complete card and account information for a customer
#   get_transactions — Get transactions for a particular account
#   validate_dispute_reason — Validate whether a dispute reason is supported
#   reclassify_dispute — Reclassify a dispute to a new reason code
#   block_card — Block a card for security
#   order_card_replacement — Order a replacement card
#   upload_documents — Upload supporting documents for a dispute
#   search_transactions_by_amount — Search transactions by amount with tolerance
#   search_transactions_by_merchant — Search transactions by merchant name
#   get_recent_transactions — Get recent transactions for a card
